tional superconductors. We develop an interferometer to prove\nentanglement of these distinguishable properties of the neutron beam by\nobserving clear violations of both Clauser-Horne-Shimony-Holt and Mermin\ncontextuality inequalities in the same experimental setup. Our work opens a\npathway to a future era of entangled neutron scattering in matter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Aug 2019 17:59:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-18"}
