 role played by\norder-parameter fluctuations in providing the key missing link between Mott\nphysics and strongly coupled toy-models exhibiting gravity duals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Aug 2019 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 May 2020 15:18:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-14"}
